// Candidate guarantees guiding the current and next verification passes.
// SPEC-GUARANTEE: Only configured governance or delegated domain/plan/oracle authority may mutate privileged controls.
// SPEC-GUARANTEE: Protocol emergency pause fails closed for reserve, claim, commitment, capital, and oracle mutations.
// SPEC-GUARANTEE: DomainAssetVault and ledger accounts remain bound to their derived reserve domain and asset mint.
// SPEC-GUARANTEE: Pending Founder commitments remain custody/pending amounts until activation books reserve capacity.
// SPEC-GUARANTEE: Reserved and settled obligation amounts never exceed approved/outstanding obligations or available reserve.
// SPEC-GUARANTEE: Claim paid_amount never exceeds approved_amount, including selected-asset payout paths.
// SPEC-GUARANTEE: Fee withdrawals never exceed accrued balances and preserve rent-exempt SOL fee-vault balances.
// SPEC-GUARANTEE: Pool class ledgers, allocation ledgers, LP positions, and redemption queues conserve shares and capacity.
// SPEC-GUARANTEE: Claim attestations bind oracle, health plan, policy series, evidence hash, schema, and claim case before oracle fees or finality are trusted.

